"{\"uid\": \"dailyhive.com-vancouver-the-flying-pig-olympic-village-closing\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Food & Drink  van  Vancouver's Olympic Village area will be down a staple restaurant come fall, as The Flying Pig Group of Restaurants will be shuttering its outpost there.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 172, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 19, \"end\": 28, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vancouver\", \"score\": 0.9999999999931788, \"rank\": 6.738665427793952e-12, \"text\": \"Vancouver\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vancouver\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vancouver\"}, {\"begin\": 31, \"end\": 46, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"score\": 0.7694335847798793, \"rank\": 0.17167788501359543, \"text\": \"Olympic Village\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Flying Pig Olympic Village (127 2nd Avenue West) confirmed to Dished it will be closing its doors in late fall.\", \"from\": 174, \"to\": 289, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We have truly enjoyed our decade-long presence in this neighbourhood, being one of the first restaurants to establish itself before the area was fully developed,\\\" the restaurant said in a statement shared with Dished.\", \"from\": 291, \"to\": 509, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Despite our efforts, we could not reach an agreement with the landlord, so we are now searching for a new location.\", \"from\": 511, \"to\": 627, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"However,Ophelia, our other establishment, will remain open, so we will still be around to serve our guests and friends in the area.\\\"\", \"from\": 628, \"to\": 760, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 636, \"end\": 643, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ophelia\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.961345588153218e-17, \"text\": \"Ophelia\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ophelia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ophelia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You might also like:Wendy's to offer $1 fry deal across Canada for National Fry DayLook Inside: One of Vancouver's most anticipated cocktail concepts opens this weekMusic icons Missy Elliott, Busta Rhymes, Ciara party in Vancouver  The Flying Pig is known for its menu of West Coast eats and comfort bites.\", \"from\": 762, \"to\": 1068, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 818, \"end\": 824, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"score\": 0.9999999817468963, \"rank\": 9.99370984223508e-09, \"text\": \"Canada\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\"}, {\"begin\": 865, \"end\": 874, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vancouver\", \"score\": 0.9999999999931788, \"rank\": 6.738665427793952e-12, \"text\": \"Vancouver\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vancouver\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vancouver\"}, {\"begin\": 939, \"end\": 944, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Missy_Elliott\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.882562298491186e-17, \"text\": \"Missy\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Missy_Elliott\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Missy_Elliott\"}, {\"begin\": 945, \"end\": 952, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bump_Elliott\", \"score\": 0.6135848929393191, \"rank\": 0.604391829539523, \"text\": \"Elliott\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bump_Elliott\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bump_Elliott\"}, {\"begin\": 954, \"end\": 966, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Busta_Rhymes\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Busta Rhymes\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Busta_Rhymes\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Busta_Rhymes\"}, {\"begin\": 968, \"end\": 973, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ciara\", \"score\": 0.9999999999979536, \"rank\": 1.956606755287038e-12, \"text\": \"Ciara\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ciara\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ciara\"}, {\"begin\": 983, \"end\": 992, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vancouver\", \"score\": 0.9999999999931788, \"rank\": 6.738665427793952e-12, \"text\": \"Vancouver\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vancouver\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vancouver\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It also has one of the most solid Happy Hours in the city, in our opinion.\", \"from\": 1069, \"to\": 1143, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The concept used to operate three locations in Vancouver; sadly, its Gastown spot was demolished after afire in its building in 2022.\", \"from\": 1145, \"to\": 1278, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1192, \"end\": 1201, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vancouver\", \"score\": 0.9999999999931788, \"rank\": 6.738665427793952e-12, \"text\": \"Vancouver\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vancouver\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vancouver\"}, {\"begin\": 1214, \"end\": 1221, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gastown\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Gastown\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gastown\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gastown\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Flying Pig Yaletown will remain open.\", \"from\": 1280, \"to\": 1321, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Be sure to head to the Olympic Village eatery this summer and fall and enjoy its fabulous patio.\", \"from\": 1322, \"to\": 1418, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1345, \